{"tid":2063263,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"經過民建聯斬人同水門雞遇襲事件之後，唔該大家隨身準備一樣野","createTime":"2020-06-13T19:18:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T14:22:35.000Z","uid":232848,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ed4be869fd255c7b36a383b34d78cde295355bd2","tid":2063263,"uid":232848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T19:18:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/06/14/030740_ede84f8ecb755be877fc334d2f175cb4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F06%2F14%2F030740_ede84f8ecb755be877fc334d2f175cb4.gif&h=0eb60c35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">就係電筒</span><br />\n最簡單可以隨時帶係身既保命架罉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Emz_1HsKmn8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEmz_1HsKmn8&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJi%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=0c1c0752\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Emz_1HsKmn8</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sVRkAEq5Brs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsVRkAEq5Brs&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJi%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=7b6310f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sVRkAEq5Brs</a><br />\n<br />\n如果比狗用電筒照過既應該就明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係正常情況下係無可能一路直視枝電筒<br />\n夜晚環境下一枝幾百流明至1000流明既電筒<br />\n已經可以保護到自己 而且遇襲個陣可以爭取到足夠既空間逃走<br />\n驚比人逗既可以買細細枝 好多體積細既電筒都好夠光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9226c6eeca46284b40faf8f022b1be3dcf953438","tid":2063263,"uid":232848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T19:19:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e8262417b4c9ecf4fb6939c76395354c9f4042","tid":2063263,"uid":232848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T19:19:38.000Z","msg":"